Relationship Between Transmission Type and MPG

Intr / Exec. Summary

Data Processing

Load necessary libraries

library(ggplot2)
library(GGally)

Loading and preprocessing the data

data(mtcars)
mtcars$am <- factor(mtcars$am, labels=c("Automatic", "Manual"))
p <- ggplot(mtcars, aes(factor(am), x=am, y=mpg, fill=am))
p + geom_boxplot() + labs(x="Transmission Type", y="MPG") + scale_fill_discrete(name="Transmission Type")

Single Variant Regression

fit <- lm(mpg~am, data = mtcars)
summary(fit)
